Package: bdverse
Title: An Infrastructural and Modular Toolkit for Biodiversity Data Quality in R
Description: The bdverse (biodiversity data universe) is a biodiversity data quality toolkit constructed as a family of R packages. It allows users with- and without programming capabilities, to conveniently and coherently employ R for data exploration, quality assessment, data cleaning, and standardization.
Version: 0.0.6
Date: 2021-07-18
